            <scopecontent id="aspace_6da2729bc66dc61fbe1b80db7d9d7e81">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The collection is organized under two headings, the Banker's Trust Company and Country files. The Banker's Trust Company folders include correspondence and memoranda concerning Browne's travels to Eastern Europe. Country files consist of Browne's background research on general economic conditions of the Soviet bloc countries.</p>
